Title: An analysis of Developer Metrics for Fault Prediction
Elements_risk_assessment:
SZZ assumes the fault was injected by the developer in the lines 
    identified as modified or deleted
UseOF-SZZ: To find when and who inject the bug
Summary:
Empirical study to analyze relationships between faults ain source code and some 
    developer metrics that can be derived from a software repository
Outcome:
fault injection rate varies among different developers and the modules touched
    by more developer contained more faults.
